    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惬意的假期，悠闲的旅程——一切本该如此。然而，一场该死的风暴彻底打破了这一切。游轮失事后，你被海水冲到了一个神秘的热带荒岛上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/5b00f7a1f73485f1fa1be24c701b830f.avif?t=1734426750\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里有广袤的沙滩，连绵的海岸线，茂密的丛林，以及似乎不那么危险的动物……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片与世隔绝的岛屿上，你将面对严峻的挑战。食物、水源、避难所，一切生存资源都得靠你亲手获取或制作。你需要探索岛屿，采集、狩猎来获取食物，通过磨练技巧来制作工具和生存所需物资，甚至需要帮助其他的遇难者一起逃出生天。你有办法生存下去吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于卡牌的荒岛生存体验</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中一切物资、工具和行动都以卡牌形式呈现，给予你独特的策略生存玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/9635984730098f41fd8d09fe6b589784.poster.avif?t=1734426750\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/9635984730098f41fd8d09fe6b589784.webm?t=1734426750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/9635984730098f41fd8d09fe6b589784.mp4?t=1734426750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>采集与狩猎，争取生存机会</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物与资源是你活下去的关键，通过采集或狩猎确保你能度过每一天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/05bc7421fd575f52f00de44f2f536041.poster.avif?t=1734426750\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/05bc7421fd575f52f00de44f2f536041.webm?t=1734426750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/05bc7421fd575f52f00de44f2f536041.mp4?t=1734426750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>结识其他幸存者</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上可能并不只有你一人，你会遇到其他幸存者——是朋友还是敌人，取决于你的判断。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164780/extras/9553263e70cee568444e5cc4a3ea3a87.avif?t=1734426750\" width=600 height=350 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种结局</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择是逃离这片荒岛，还是在这里建立新家园，故事的结局由你亲手书写。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座孤岛上，挑战生存的极限，同时发掘属于你的冒险故事。</p>",
